QuestData.Title: WANTED: Gutsmash the Destroyer
QuestData.Description: Gutsmash has proven to be more than a worthy adversary. Gather a small group together and end his reign of terror once and for all.
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill Gutsmash the Destroyer in Frostfire Ridge.
QuestData.RewardText: Gutsmash is dead? I'll drink to that. You're alright, $n.
